(3) [System setting] => [Brightness & Lock] => [Turn screen off when inactive for: 1 hour]
(4) [Terminal] => [Preferences] => [Profiles] => [Edit] => [Custom font] => [14]
(5) 

2. Sougou
(1) [System setting] => [Language Support]
(2) "The language support is not installed completely" => [Install]
(3) [Keyboard input method system: IBus] => [fcitx]
(4) ch@dell:~/Downloads$ sudo dpkg -i sogoupinyin_2.2.0.0102_amd64.deb
(5) ch@dell:~/Downloads$ sudo apt-get -f install 
(6) ch@dell:~/Downloads$ sudo dpkg -i sogoupinyin_2.2.0.0102_amd64.deb
(7) ch@dell:~/Downloads$ reboot
## 18.04:
(1) [System setting] => [Region & Language] => [Manage Installed Languages]
(2) 双击下载的 deb 软件包，即可直接安装搜狗输入法。
(3) [Keyboard input method system: IBus] => [fcitx]
(4) [Applications] => [Fcitx] => [Fcitx Configure]
(4) [Applications] => [Fcitx Configure] => "+" => turn off "Only Show Current Language" => "Sogou Pinyin" => "^"

3. VIM
(1) sudo apt-get update
(2) sudo apt-get upgrade
(3) sudo apt-get dist-upgrade
(4) sudo apt-get install vim
(5) 

4. Sublime Text (apt)
(1) Install the GPG key:
    wget -qO - https://download.sublimetext.com/sublimehq-pub.gpg | sudo apt-key add -
(2) Ensure apt is set up to work with https sources:
    sudo apt-get install apt-transport-https
(3) Select the channel to use:
    [Stable]
    echo "deb https://download.sublimetext.com/ apt/stable/" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/sublime-text.list
    [Dev]
    echo "deb https://download.sublimetext.com/ apt/dev/" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/sublime-text.list
(4) Update apt sources and install Sublime Text:
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get install sublime-text
(5) 安装包SyncedSidebarBg，自动同步侧边栏底色为编辑窗口底色。

